        </div>
        <div class="cl"></div>
        </div>
        <!--地铁——现房-->
        <div class="tit-bottom">
            <span>地铁——现房</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-fy">
            开车太堵坐车太慢，还是坐地铁吧。2016年开始楼市也将真正迎来地铁时代，小编为大家精心挑选了以下楼盘，看看哪个楼盘更合你心意！
        </div>
        <div class="fyinfo">
            <div class="right">
               <ul>
                    {% if push_dtxf is defined %}
                        {% for item in push_dtxf %}
                            {% set dtxfAttrs = ('house.houses')|getRow({id: item.fromid|default(''), checked: 1, findType: 1}) %}
                                <li>
                                    <a href="{{('houses/detail')|U({id: item.fromid|default('')})}}" target="_blank">
                                       {{core_global.lazy_img({
                                            width: 339,
                                            height: 211,
                                            src: item.thumb|default(''),
                                            alt: item.name|default(''),
                                            type: 2
                                        })}}
                                       </a>
                                    <div class="name">
                                        <span>{{ core_global.formField({value: item.lcs|default(''), form: 'lcs', field: 'lcs', tpl: '%title%&nbsp;'}) }}
                                           {{item.dj|default('')}}元/平起</span>
                                        <a href="{{('houses/detail')|U({id: item.fromid|default('')})}}" target="_blank">{{item.name|default('')}}</a>
                                        <div class="cl"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="jiaofang">{{dtxfAttrs.attributes.jfrq.value|default('更新中...')}}交房</div>
                                </li>

                        {% endfor %}
                    {% endif %}
                    <div class="cl"></div>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="cl"></div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="cl"></div>

